Vector::Object3D Version 0.01
=============================

Vector::Object3D is Perl module providing most basic procedures to facilitate
handling of vector object calculations in the 3D space, including fundamental
transformations as well as perspective 2D casting.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

